verse.name: v1a
verse.lines:
If You don’t help me where else can I go
No where, No where
If you don’t heal me where else can I go
No where, No where

verse.name: v1b
verse.lines:
So I run to You
So I run to You
I run to You
I run to You

verse.name: v1c
verse.lines:
And I run to You
(Running)
I run to You Jesus
I run to You
I’m running to You
